{{#layout}}
<h1>OAuth2 / OpenID Connect Login Demo</h1>

This page showcases MockLab's simulation of a generic OAuth2 / OpenID Connect login provider, hosted at
<a href="https://openid-connect.mocklab.io" title="MockLab OAuth2 simulation">https://openid-connect.mocklab.io</a>.

<div style="display: flex; margin-top: 20px">
    <div class="demo-box">
        <p>
            The OAuth2 flow uses the <code>authorization_code</code> grant type and fetches the user profile from the <code>/userinfo</code> endpoint.
        </p>
        <p>
            <a href="/oauth2/authorization/mock-oauth2" class="login-start-button">
                <img src="/images/oauth-2-logo.png" alt="OAuth2 logo"/>
                Login with OAuth2
            </a>
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="demo-box">
        <p>
            The OpenID Connect flow also uses the <code>authorization_code</code> grant type and requests an JWT ID token from which
            the user profile is retrieved.
        </p>
        <p>
            <a href="/oauth2/authorization/mock-oidc" class="login-start-button">
                <img src="/images/openid-icon-100x100.png" alt="OpenID Connect logo" />
                Login with OpenID Connect
            </a>
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
{{/layout}}